<div id="main-visual" class="d-flex align-items-center" >
  <ul>
    <li class="justify-content-center"><%= image_tag "img/donut.jpg", class: "feed-images mx-auto w-100" %></li>
    <li><%= image_tag "img/cake.jpg", class: "mx-auto w-100" %></li>
    <li><%= image_tag "img/cupcakes1.jpg", class: "mx-auto w-100" %></li>
  </ul>
</div>
<ul class="slider mx-auto w-100">
  <li><a href="#" class="opacity-2 text-dark font-weight-bold" data-turbolinks='false'>【夏ギフト】あの人にも。長野の夏、届けます。</a></li>
  <li><a href="#" class="text-dark font-weight-bold" data-turbolinks='false'>【7/11(木)販売】「山根フルーツ農園」とのスペシャルコラボ商品販売開始。</a></li>
  <li><a href="#" class="text-dark font-weight-bold" data-turbolinks='false'>【大人気商品】バターサンド詰め合わせ。オンライン限定商品も。</a></li>
</ul>
<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <%= render 'public/items/genre', genres: @genres %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9">
        <div class="mx-auto mt-5">
          <h2>新着商品</h2>
          <div class="row">
            <% @items.each do |item| %>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <%= link_to public_item_path(item) do %>
                <%= attachment_image_tag item, :image, :fill, 200, 200, fallback: "", class: "img-fluid float1" %>
              <% end %>
              <p><%= link_to item.name, public_item_path(item), class: "text-dark" %></p>
              <p>¥<%= item.price %></p>
            </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <p class="text-right"><%= link_to ">>全ての商品を見る", public_items_path, class: "text-dark" %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
